The paper presents an approach to integrating machine learning into programming languages, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the integration of this approach into the standard software development workflow, which relates to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the paper mentions the use of reinforcement learning in their implementation, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
